        public SentenceStream(java.io.File conllFile,
                      java.lang.String[] columns,
                      java.lang.String separator)
               throws java.io.IOException
        Creates a new reader for a CoNLL-format file.
        Parameters:
        conllFile - the file to be read
        columns - an array whose dimension is equal to the number of columns in the CoNLL file, and whosse i-th element is a label for the i-th column of the file, or null if that column is to be ignored
        separator - the separator between fields in the conll file.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException
